fivetodos: Hi and welcome! I am Gossik and I will try my best to help you get your things done and make your dreams come true. In the next days I will show you step by step how I work and we can get to know us.
gettingToKnowPush: We are still in the process of getting to know each other. Therefore I will send you push notifications once in a while to learn when you want to do what - or do nothing at all. In the meantime, you can use the 'Do' page anytime to input your available time and I will try to suggest you the optimal doable task for you based on how I know you.

thoughts: Hi and welcome on the 'Organize' page. Often people remember things that need to be done or should not be forgotten, but they don't have time to deal with it and therefore forget it later. This happens to me on a daily basis. To avoid forgetting these things, you can open me and save a thought within 5 seconds only. Like this, you can deal with it later when you have time. Here you can see all your saved thoughts and add new ones by clicking on the big '+' icon. With me, you'll never forget anything again!
